# Slash commands ↔ rules

Commands live under `.cursor/commands/`. Type `/` in chat to run one (restart Cursor if it doesn’t appear).

| Slash command | File | Use with |
|---------------|------|----------|
| **trace-upstream** | `trace-upstream.md` | `upstream-first-debugging.mdc` (same five steps) |
| **pre-deploy-sweep** | `pre-deploy-sweep.md` | `outcome-minimal-steps-framing.mdc` (answer/report shape); `upstream-first-debugging.mdc` (constraints) |

**trace-upstream** — Debug/fix: trace config/schema/env before app code. **pre-deploy-sweep** — Release readiness on the current branch.
